that side, get that up.

05:12.487 --> 05:13.887
I got this,
you get down there now.

05:13.889 --> 05:15.088
I got this, you
get down there, go!

05:15.090 --> 05:17.156
- Go, go, go, go!
- All right, we've got one.

05:17.158 --> 05:19.394
Do it from inside.

05:22.163 --> 05:23.997
All right.

05:23.999 --> 05:25.098
All right, you
taut, everybody good?

05:27.302 --> 05:29.069
All right, nice job, fellas.

05:48.590 --> 05:50.055
We good?

05:50.057 --> 05:52.024
Ah, our Father.

05:52.026 --> 05:54.127
Air velocity is...

05:54.129 --> 05:55.362
- Lord in heaven.
- Now it's comin' up.

05:55.364 --> 05:56.930
Hallowed be thy name.

05:56.932 --> 05:58.098
Thy kingdom come,
thy will be done

05:58.100 --> 05:59.199
