05:59.201 --> 06:00.165
- Good job, John, good job.
- Hallowed be thy name.

06:00.167 --> 06:02.201
Thy kingdom, Earth.

06:02.203 --> 06:06.072
Give us this daily bread and
forgive us our trespasses

06:06.074 --> 06:07.607
