06:11.612 --> 06:16.552
and the glory forever, amen.

06:18.287 --> 06:22.225
It's all good.

06:30.999 --> 06:32.499
Boys, we're sittin'
here talkin' in circles.

06:32.501 --> 06:34.567
Ain't none of us really
come up with somethin'.

06:34.569 --> 06:36.036
We gotta figure it out.

06:36.038 --> 06:37.405
Well I say we go.

06:39.074 --> 06:42.041
It ain't nothin' but free
heat's the way I look at it.

06:42.043 --> 06:43.076
And I don't give a good goddamn

06:43.078 --> 06:44.576
what my brother
finds down there.

06:44.578 --> 06:46.112
Excuse me, John.

06:46.114 --> 06:47.213
Yeah.

06:47.215 --> 06:49.382
Paycheck's more important
than gettin' shut down.

06:49.384 --> 06:52.218
Well we all need to put
food on our table, ya know?

06:52.220 --> 06:54.086
My family needs me
to work, ya know?

06:54.088 --> 06:54.923
We all do.

06:58.160 --> 07:00.392
Paycheck ain't gon'
mean shit if you die

07:00.394 --> 07:02.264
two miles in, Kenny.

07:04.499 --> 07:06.232
Now we are filled
up with more methane

07:06.234 --> 07:09.101
than any other
mine in this area.

07:09.103 --> 07:11.504
If you call MSHA
and they come down

07:11.506 --> 07:13.740
