that fuckin' mine,

07:13.742 --> 07:16.175
they gon' shut us
down methane or not.

07:16.177 --> 07:18.144
And what's he gonna do?

07:18.146 --> 07:19.512
Smitty, what are you gon' do?

07:19.514 --> 07:20.547
Tiny, what are you gon' do?

07:20.549 --> 07:22.081
There ain't no fuckin' thing

07:22.083 --> 07:23.149
- to do around here!
- That mine is a bomb, Kenny!

07:23.151 --> 07:26.485
And we are all sittin'
right in the middle of it!

07:26.487 --> 07:28.221
God's gonna protect us, hm?

07:28.223 --> 07:31.559
God will not protect
us in Hell, John.

07:34.028 --> 07:38.298
Now you've all seen
it, shift after shift.

07:38.300 --> 07:42.267
It's gettin' worse and
worse, bigger and bigger.

07:42.269 --> 07:44.704
Zeke, if I die down
below my family's

07:44.706 --> 07:46.605
gonna get insurance.

07:46.607 --> 07:48.608
Me up here without a job?

07:48.610 --> 07:50.679
Hell, man, I'm worthless.

07:54.148 --> 07:56.149
Well, fellas, the
sump pump in the section

07:56.151 --> 07:58.254
can't keep up, all right?

07:59.453 --> 08:01.021
And when it fails
we're gon' drown.

08:01.023 --> 08:02.254
You wanna add that to the list?

08:02.256 --> 08:05.124
You wanna add that
to the raft of shit!

08:05.126 --> 08:08.093
I ain't blowed up or
drowned in 15 years.

08:08.095 --> 08:10.163
Now I ain't scared, I ain't
tellin' y'all what to be.

08:10.165 --> 08:13.102
What kinda fuckin'
logic is that?

08:14.268 --> 08:18.173
Now all in favor of
diggin' some coal, say aye.

08:22.511 --> 08:24.177
Aye.

08:24.179 --> 08:25.014
