08:46.201 --> 08:50.338
Kenny, Ryan shouldn't be
goin' down there with us.

08:52.239 --> 08:53.372
You fellas have a nice night.

08:53.374 --> 08:55.475
What my boy does is none
of your goddamn business,

08:55.477 --> 08:56.642
big brother.

08:56.644 --> 08:57.610
Hey, hey, hey, hey.

08:57.612 --> 08:59.215
- Easy.
- Let it go.

09:01.115 --> 09:02.815
