are waterproof.

13:09.496 --> 13:10.997
That mine goes a hell of
a lot deeper underground

13:10.999 --> 13:13.031
than the water table is.

13:13.033 --> 13:15.638
What's the water table again?

13:17.471 --> 13:20.806
It is the lowest point
to where the water sits.

13:20.808 --> 13:21.773
It's geology.

13:21.775 --> 13:23.508
- On me, me.
- Okay.

13:23.510 --> 13:25.411
Look, the stream is
no more than 60 feet deep.

13:25.413 --> 13:27.579
Rivers, lakes, wells,
no more 'n 200 feet.

13:27.581 --> 13:30.550
