2,000 feet deep.

13:30.552 --> 13:32.617
We take on water, that's
just the way it is.

13:32.619 --> 13:34.920
Okay, I'm so confused.

13:34.922 --> 13:36.555
I told him all that.

13:36.557 --> 13:38.657
